data.description: This home has so much to offer in every aspect! Set on a quarter acre corner lot in the beautiful Riverwalk subdivision, you can enjoy spectacular panoramic VIEWS from your home. In addition, the exterior has 3 sides masonry, rain gutters along all 4 sides and lovely fruit trees in the back yard. The floor plan belies the square footage with 3 spacious bedrooms AND a large office which can double as your 4th bedroom or guest room. Nice sized kitchen with granite countertops, mosaic backsplash and beautiful wood cabinets, overlooks the well appointed living room. Amenities in this lovely neighborhood include a pool just steps across the street. The elementary school, Riverwalk park, the soccer fields and Hutto Lake Park, with trails, birdwatching, picnicking and fishing are a short walk away. If that's not enough, its an easy commute in any direction with quick access to toll 130/45 and Highway 79.
